be\u7f6eSELinux\u5bbd\u5bb9\n`fastboot continue`##\u5728FASTBOOT\u4e2d\u76f4\u63a5\u5f15\u5bfc\u7cfb\u7edf\n\n2. **\u5728\u7cfb\u7edf\u4e2d\u8fdb\u884c\uff1a\uff08\u4f9d\u6b21\uff09**\n`adb push ksud /data/local/tmp/`\n`adb shell chmod 777 /data/local/tmp/ksud`\n`adb shell service call miui.mqsas.IMQSNative 21 i32 1 s16 '/data/local/tmp/ksud' i32 1 s16 'late-load' s16 '/sdcard/ksulog.txt' i32 60` ##\u6f0f\u6d1e\u63d0\u6743\n\u81f3\u6b64\u6210\u529f\n\n`adb shell su -c setenforce 1`##\u6062\u590dSELinux\u4e25\u683c\n\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1773287466, "style": "<style>.markdown-alert{padding:0.5rem 1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:.25em solid var(--borderColor-default,var(--color-border-default));}.markdown-alert .markdown-alert-title {display:flex;font-weight:var(--base-text-weight-medium,500);align-items:center;line-height:1;}.markdown-alert>:first-child {margin-top:0;}.markdown-alert>:last-child {margin-bottom:0;}</style><style>.markdown-alert.markdown-alert-important {border-left-color:var(--borderColor-done-emphasis, var(--color-done-emphasis));background-color:var(--color-done-subtle);}.markdown-alert.markdown-alert-important .markdown-alert-title {color: var(--fgColor-done,var(--color-done-fg));}</style>", "script": "", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://pic.jiayv.wang/file/shit/1770022438673_1766420097264.webp", "createdDate": "2026-03-12", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}}, "singeListJson": {}, "labelColorDict": {"good first issue": "#7057ff", "help wanted": "#008672", "invalid": "#e4e669", "question": "#d876e3", "\u4e00\u822c\u5185\u5bb9": "#cfd3d7", "\u6742\u8c08": "#c5def5", "\u7ea2\u6e29": "#d73a4a", "\u8d44\u6e90": "#0075ca"}, "displayTitle": "\u9e7f\u9e23\u753a\u5c4b", "faviconUrl": "https://pic.jiayv.wang/file/shit/1770022438673_1766420097264.webp", "ogImage": "https://pic.jiayv.wang/file/shit/1770022438673_1766420097264.webp", "primerCSS": "<link href='https://mirrors.sustech.edu.cn/cdnjs/ajax/libs/Primer/21.0.7/primer.css' rel='stylesheet' />", 